{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act12side", "eventName": "多索雷斯假日", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DH-8", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "搶灘登陸", "storyInfo": "坎黛拉感謝星熊等人的行動，並邀請她們留下。\n船上，陳和林雨霞一番討論後，決定了行動方針。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "20_I00", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkalley_intro", "key": "$darkalley_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_npc_198_1#4", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，聽得到嗎，聽得到嗎？", "name": "坎黛拉"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "親愛的市民朋友們，還有遊客朋友們，是我，坎黛拉。", "name": "坎黛拉"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "首先，不用太緊張。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不得不說，老潘喬這一齣完全在我的預想之外。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怎麼想得到我信任的手下居然一直密謀著奪取我的城市這麼可怕的事呢，這太可怕了！", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，正如我一開始所說的，這並不是什麼值得驚慌的事。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不如說，我要感謝老潘喬才行。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老實說，這兩年，我也一直在思考，怎樣才能讓大獎賽變得更加刺激，更加引人注目，更加能讓人從中獲得快樂。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我一直沒有找到特別好的方法。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而老潘喬為我找到了，他用自己的行動向我展示了一場更加刺激的大獎賽！", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大獎賽結束了？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，恰恰相反。就在剛剛那一刻，本次大獎賽進入了真正的高潮！", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有隊伍在此時都將復活，競猜環節將會重新啟動。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盡可能地去阻止那些在城裡鬧事的傢伙們，我知道你們有這個本事。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事情結束後，我會給你們應有的獎賞。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_197_1#7"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#7"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#2"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#2"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#4", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，就是你們兩個吧，我的手下們說，你們在剛才幫他們擋住了一波針對我的刺殺。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來吧，請坐，作為對你們的褒獎，你們也在這特等座和我一起享受這場比賽吧。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_197_1#4"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您......是認真的？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#4"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當然是認真的。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老潘喬知道，在我面前掀桌子的話，他的贏面很小。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以他縮在了這艘我交給他保管的船上。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是我沒猜錯的話，他應該私底下給這艘船加了不少東西，大炮之類的？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#5"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，如果只是這樣的話，其實沒有那麼有威脅吧？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#5"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第二輪比賽和第三輪比賽期間，會邀請許多來自各方的權貴上船，讓他們能夠用自己的雙眼體會比賽的樂趣。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我懂了，這些權貴的性命才是關鍵。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為這座城市的運轉需要和這些人打交道。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對對對，現在就不是我想不想解決他的問題，而是那些老爺的手下們希不希望我立刻解決他的問題。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖嘖，陣仗搞得這麼大，結果還是來陰的嘛。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多半是埃內斯托那小子教他的。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正如你們所見，現在我能做的事情並不多，但是，實際上他能做的事情也不多。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，為什麼不把事情變得更加有趣一點呢？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是這不是會更加刺激他......", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他要是真的敢把那些老爺拉出來斃了，我就算把這座城市讓給他又怎麼樣？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不明白，Missy，他既然想要奪取這座城市去打仗，那終究也是要仰仗那些老爺的。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#6"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然他打仗的錢和士兵哪裡來？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#6"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真要我說，船上那些老爺裡，恐怕早有幾個和他已經談好的了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#6"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#2"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？你們兩個年輕人很有意思啊，看打扮，不是玻利瓦爾人？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，我們來自龍門，現在還有兩個朋友在船上。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？你們兩個竟然是陳世侄和林世侄的朋友？怎麼沒有聽她們提起過。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們沒有告訴她們，是偷偷來玩的，您不知道自然也正常。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈，原來如此。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然如此，我可以多告訴你們一點——", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我將這件事委託給了陳世侄與林世侄，而另一方面，我答應了文月夫人，她們兩人在這裡不會受到任何危險。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們知道這意味著什麼嗎？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "意味著還不到時候。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很懂啊，東國的姑娘。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果兩位世侄真的有什麼閃失，那船上的那些老爺們，可就要給可憐的老潘喬陪葬了。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#4"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Missy，別怕。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來來來，正所謂不打不相識，來，坐，我們好好聊聊。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G06", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_1013_spchen_1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "解決了？", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "解決了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是情況確實不妙。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，你去對付埃內斯托，我來調查的分工還是太晚了。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒錯。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不甘心？", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不甘心......但也沒辦法。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這件事沒那麼簡單，早有預感的不是嗎。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒想到會鬧這麼大。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怕了？", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼可能。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在在哪？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "某個船艙裡。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你和埃內斯托聊天的時候，我到處走了走，雖然在潘喬開始行動前船上氣氛還算輕鬆。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過在潘喬演講之後，船上的那些船員和水手立刻開始行動了。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在船上戒備非常森嚴，而且武裝和補給非常充足。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經做好了拉鋸戰的準備了嗎。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，也不是完全沒辦法。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼說？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外，他們把船上那些權貴都關到了一間房間裡。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是劫匪很常見的做法......等等。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從人質下手吧。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你也發現了。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使船上有再多的武器和再多的補給，以及陸地上準備了再多的接應，最多我想也只能和掌控著這座城市的坎黛拉女士打成平手。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一旦時間拉長，他勝算並不大。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些權貴人質才是他的護身符。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，沒錯，這些權貴全都是來自三方政府的大人物。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作為人質，他們能夠起到很好的掣肘作用。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不需要很長時間，只需要一小會，只要能讓坎黛拉女士在這段時間裡有所猶豫。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他就能做更多的事，也將有更多的籌碼。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我們只有兩個人。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說白了，我並不是很想玩你那種個人英雄主義的戲碼。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來做。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "救人交給你，我來幫你分散他們的注意。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也可以。船上應該有那種救生小船，再不濟讓他們跳海就是了。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後呢？", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼然後？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你打算救了人就跑？", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你打算一個人留在船上逞英雄的話，我不攔你。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵。那就這樣吧。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，開始？", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開始吧。對了，電話別掛，保持通信。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203,