: {"content": "哥哥，你沒事吧？", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你被那個姓陳的打暈了。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，對，我想起來了......", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在是什麼情況？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事情正在按照我們計畫的進行，已經有幾個老爺同意協助爸爸了。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，陳小姐呢？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在把你打暈後，好像在船上四處引發混亂，爸爸已經下令捉拿她了。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "引發混亂......不對。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉菲艾拉，你現在快帶人去關押人質的地方看看情況。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我恐怕陳小姐現在是在為林小姐創造機會。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是讓她們劫走人質就糟了。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，哥哥你......", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒事，快去。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好哦。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "埃內斯托"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "zoom", "xpos": 0.5, "ypos": 0.3, "scale": 1.5, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G06", "xScale": 1.7, "yScale": 1.7, "x": 200.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "xTo": 100.0, "duration": 25.0, "ease": "1", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有個老朋友說過，只有被狠狠捶打過一遍，我才會像過去的她一樣，知道自己那些可笑的執著都不過是些衝動。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我到現在也還沒有分清，哪些是可以堅持的執著，哪些是不切實際的衝動。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我想她應該也是知道的，如果因此我就不去做的話，我也就不叫陳暉潔了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真好啊，陳小姐，你知道自己在做什麼，也知道該怎麼做。", "name": "埃內斯托"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我呢。", "name": "埃內斯托"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G06", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, 